00:02:28.927 --> 00:02:30.110
with a few spare.

00:02:31.044 --> 00:02:32.993
So that's exactly what we did.

00:02:33.017 --> 00:02:36.091
We divided the world
into three-meter squares,

00:02:36.115 --> 00:02:38.956
gave each one a unique,
three-word identifier --

00:02:38.980 --> 00:02:40.712
what we call a three-word address.

00:02:41.385 --> 00:02:44.457
So for example, right here,

00:02:44.481 --> 00:02:46.676
I'm standing at mustards.coupons.pinup,

00:02:46.858 --> 00:02:48.008
(Laughter)

00:02:48.032 --> 00:02:49.883
but over here ...

00:02:50.753 --> 00:02:53.701
I'm standing at pinched.
singularly.tutorial.

